name: Stephane Tetsing
description: Stephane Tetsing is a AI software engineer and researcher at the forefront of integrating artificial intelligence with Web3 technologies. His unique background in Healthcare AI has positioned him as a figure in the emerging field of decentralized secure systems and privacy-preserving data analysis. Stephane recently led development of a custom LLM for the Remix Toolset called SolCoder, and is now working on improvements and research into other language integrations
